such as how the military should be involved in the campaign and 
whether the death penalty should be imposed when a police officer 
or other people are killed as a result of drug trafficking 
our task force should agree on solutions for every area of the 
drug problem from blocking supplies to curtailing demand from 
treatment to education to prosecution from interdiction and 
confiscation to eradication nothing should be overlooked or ruled 
out the president said 
