12day south american tour in which he condemned drugs in bolivia 
preached reconciliation in peru and paraguay and reminded uruguay 
of its roman catholic roots 
the pontiffs plane arrived at romes ciampino airport shortly 
after 4 pm and he headed directly for the vatican 
he ended his tour in the paraguayan capital of asuncion on 
