didnt know where she was going to stay 
the squat she had stayed in the night before was set afire by 
someone looking for a girl named star she said he says 
hell keep burning places down until he finds star 
mimi said shed like to be a model and that she left home 
because her father tried to rape her she said she met a sweet 
boy who gave her a gold ring the boy is about twice her age 
another girl at children of the night said that during her years 
