moved her into an apartment 
they gave me my food they washed my clothes and gave me an 
id said the girl who called herself cheryl i hung out for a 
couple of months until i got sick of it 
cheryl says she is off the streets and going to school 
yates hocking and ms lee say young people can be rescued each 
