shares he parked at jefferies amp co leaving the los angeles 
securities firm with a 250000 loss the paper said 
later however bilzerian partly reimbursed jefferies and then 
sent the firm two phony invoices for 75000 each when he leared 
the firm had recouped a good portion of the loss on its own the 
journal said 
in his next deal the paper said the florida raider secretly 
enlisted the aid of the debartolo in his bid for cluett peabody amp 
co sec documents do not reveal any links between the two but the 
